				<div class="TU"><br><ul><li>The DNA fragments containing the complete promoter regions of class II and III genes [ trg ( Fig. 2 ) and ﬂiC , ﬂgB , ﬂiA ( not shown ) ] were tested in the same way as for gel retardation by LrhA .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=12123461" target="_blank">12123461</a>]<br></li>
